headline.print_headline: Rates Rise at Weekly US Treasury Bill Auction
headline.main: Rates Rise at Weekly US Treasury Bill Auction

lead_paragraph: Interest rates on short-term Treasury bills rose in Monday's auction with rates on six-month bills climbing to their highest level in more than two years.
